  m_text: "You can change all of theres for custom gamemod:\n\nBackground: mods/CustomGame/world.png
    (1920x1080)\nTree: mods/CustomGame/tree.png (720x720)\nMusic: mods/CustomGame/bgm.mp3\nLot
    of settings: /mods/CustomGame/Settings.json\n\nEnemies: \nmods/CustomGame/Enemies/{name}_Enemy.json\nmods/CustomGame/Enemies/{name}_Enemy.png
    (720x720)\n---You can add as much as enemy you want---\n\n*Note: Unchnaged texture
    files are using default Black-Purple textures. And at least one enemy is needed"
